divs: Sighting DetailsWe were smoking some pot when it happened. The object flew from left to right but some of us thought it flew from right to left. Who will ever know what happened ! It was scary at the time but the next day it was mysteriously not there anymore. I still have nightmares about it. Perhaps it was the Russians or the Chinese. Someone is watching us - that I know. Pass the dutchie from the left hand side.
